Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is, is there a difference between God, or the Creator, and the true self?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And if so, or is there a difference in quality?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.04,0:01:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The capital S is the radiance of God as experienced, you know, in the human domain, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.43,0:01:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's sort of like the emanation of God?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, when you were talking about earlier that the dilemma of human, of being here is
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.95,0:01:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,whether we're going to worship the narcissistic core, the ego, or God.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.61,0:01:33.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's the dilemma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.01,0:01:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the true self that's deciding between those two options?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.05,0:01:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the true self that attracts you to seeking the truth in the first place, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.12,0:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The ego separates off as an individual, which is not the absolute truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:02:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So the self is not satisfied with that until you transcend that illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it keeps you on the path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.18,0:02:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I felt it kind of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The gravity of God pulls all your little molecules.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for a dozen people here, or what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.46,0:02:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I really appreciate being able to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never expressed my gratitude for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.68,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the whole experience, the people here, and it's been a great source of inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.90,0:02:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.60,0:02:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.72,0:02:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.02,0:02:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming quite a bit this year, and I want to thank you, Susan,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,for your devotion to truth and to Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.26,0:03:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And Dr. Hawkins, I want to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I was introduced to your teachings in about March of last year,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and I had been struggling with being an honest person, being more honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and your teachings have given me the courage to be more honest and live more honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.16,0:03:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.60,0:03:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,As I've been practicing, this year I recognized this little whining, bawling child within me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've been practicing the Zen thing of just recognizing the childishness when it comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.12,0:03:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and trying not to judge it and allow it to go through its process.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.56,0:03:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have started recently becoming really paranoid when the childishness comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.56,0:03:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And being paranoid that, oh, who saw that, oh, you know, did somebody see me be childish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,or is somebody picking up on my childishness?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And how do I handle that paranoia?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you do it like a parent would with a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.86,0:04:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You can parent the child within yourself, see, and say, yes, I hear you and I understand how you see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.42,0:04:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But now we have to give that up and see it as an adult sees it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's the adult in my mind talking to the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.74,0:04:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And the child in the mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.06,0:04:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.70,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're different archetypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.34,0:04:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The adult, the parent, and the child are different archetypes in the Jungian sense of archetypes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.37,0:04:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.51,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.09,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I talk about that in weight reduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in weight reduction, I always say, put a label on your refrigerator that says adults only.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the minute you sit down to eat, the child comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw that in a dignified businessman in a cafeteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.59,0:05:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,He sits down, and here's a dignified businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And as he starts to look at his tray, you can see the child come up in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The child came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.66,0:05:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very comical.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.42,0:05:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So the adult in you says, I'm going to watch my calories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you open the refrigerator, the child comes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The adult disappears.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,After the child has indulged himself, then the parent comes up in you and says, how could you have been so stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.86,0:05:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You just ate 300 calories, idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So once you see that's the interplay between those archetypes within the unconscious, and make them conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you put a sign on your refrigerator that says, adults only.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Adults only.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.07,0:05:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,First, thank you for all your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been very helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.61,0:06:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, so helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.69,0:06:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about directing attention through visualization of goals, as you pointed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can it be called conscious creation?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.26,0:06:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be pushing it a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And any idea of what is the calibration of doing the visualization of goals?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what I'm saying is the ego can really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.25,0:06:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,grasp it like, now I have a way to...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you have to select, you know, you have to look over what the goal is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.77,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the time to look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.69,0:06:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because once you start giving it energy, then it's going to tend to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to choose what you think is worth putting the energy in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.54,0:06:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's say you want to live in a certain kind of house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.88,0:07:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What you do is you picture the house and you picture the setting, and you just hold that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.92,0:07:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you do that, it tends to materialize.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, if you picture yourself being the chief of evil, I guess you'd have to, you know, question yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.90,0:07:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is that a good thing to hold in mind, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.16,0:07:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no cause of anything as it in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But as I put my attention on it, it tends to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.70,0:07:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Materialize, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.36,0:07:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's depending on context.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.20,0:07:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,See, the idea of cause is within content.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a this doing a that causing a that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's another way things can happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.60,0:07:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the most optimal conditions, the seed tends to flourish, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So you provide the optimal conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And under the optimal conditions, you tend to manifest that which you're envisioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:08:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So envisioning does have an effect on outcome, but it does not cause an effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.23,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It plays a part, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.33,0:08:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Things are really propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.61,0:08:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Propensities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,For propensity to actualize depends on local conditions as well as general conditions, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.50,0:08:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hoping you can explain this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like every time I come here or I get a new insight or a glimpse of something higher,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.30,0:08:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I get just something will happen in the external world and I just get flattened.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And is this a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that work?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.10,0:09:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time you seem to be pulling ahead, you fall behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This last month was just the whole month.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we all said that periods, you know, you work through some negative karma, you come out into a nice positive place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That now gives permission for the next stack to come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual progression is not a straight line.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So when you're riding over your karma, you're feeling good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.56,0:09:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But that now gives, the self takes advantage of that and now brings up the next stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.56,0:09:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you feel like you're going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.56,0:09:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not actually going down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.56,0:09:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You now have the strength to handle the next stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It does not feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You must say, thank you God for allowing me to handle the next stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.46,0:09:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have had some experiences out of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.71,0:10:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where I have prayed and felt something higher just lift me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.71,0:10:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The prayer wasn't to change the circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.71,0:10:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The prayer was, help me see it differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.00,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And so I think the first time that I ever prayed that way, something did happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.00,0:10:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you might say, spiritual progression comes in waves.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Where you feel like you're above it and then suddenly that brings up the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.30,0:10:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I made great progress before I hit hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.76,0:10:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,See now you have the strength to handle the worst of all possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.34,0:10:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's really God's confirmation of his confidence in your ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That you can handle this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it would have destroyed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's also another premise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.06,0:11:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never given more than you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.06,0:11:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never given more than you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You feel like you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But it doesn't mean that you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.15,0:11:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard that before but I didn't know if that was a true statement or just.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think it's a true statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're never given more than you can handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.31,0:11:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you think you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.00,0:11:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can but that's an illusion, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.00,0:11:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.70,0:11:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because you think you can't that you didn't handle it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You say, oh I can't handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.74,0:11:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The person you were at that time couldn't have handled that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.74,0:11:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But the person you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.74,0:11:47.74,Default,,0,0,0,,With conviction, determination and some spiritual experience under your belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, can handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's a vote of confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can even handle chewing gum after a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.94,0:12:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, first of all I want to thank you very much for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.58,0:12:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Life has definitely changed for the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I have a question that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.83,0:12:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably needs some recontextualization so I'll try to read it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.83,0:12:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In the new book you mention that seriously committed devotees end up with challenges such as.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The seriously committed devotees end up with challenges such as surrendering attachments to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Possessions, lifestyles, concepts such as obligation and responsibilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that in my life I have a responsibility and obligation to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.83,0:12:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,My child and my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.83,0:13:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like for you to help me recontextualize that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.83,0:13:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is your conflict between the two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.25,0:13:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm pulled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.25,0:13:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you pulled? I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In business are you tempted to be dishonest?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.40,0:13:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.40,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tempted to provide the best for the people you love?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.40,0:13:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the conflict?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.28,0:13:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that in business that I can't take decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.47,0:13:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Clear decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.47,0:13:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't make clear decisions in business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.47,0:13:35.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have a partner or a consultant?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.37,0:13:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anybody you confide in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well yeah, I have some people I can talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well you confide in them and of course you see what we do is we often use the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.37,0:13:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We ask is this in the highest good?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.37,0:13:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, we get invited to speak all kinds of places.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The first thing we do is say, you know, this is integrous, this will serve the highest good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.56,0:14:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll ask, would this work in our life right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that's something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.59,0:14:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It may be a good thing but you may get that the timing is not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a time that you, I think what I'm leading to is, is there a time that you give up everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.91,0:14:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he's worried about giving up everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And his family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.36,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there comes a time when it's not a decision, it's what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.36,0:14:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You can raise your family and continue your business by your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.45,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your business while your family's growing and then still.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you become spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.45,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,There comes a time that it's overwhelming and overpowering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And you don't have to make a decision, you just can't go there anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.45,0:14:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.09,0:14:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:14:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.41,0:15:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel so grateful and blessed to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.41,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I wanted to thank you for making yourself available to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.41,0:15:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.63,0:15:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question is, I wonder if you could elaborate a little on how to surrender your
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,sexuality to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.63,0:15:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender your sexuality to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants to know how you surrender your sexuality to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you mean sexual drive?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.63,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.63,0:15:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How can, how do you turn it over to God so it serves that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.63,0:15:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see that it's autonomous, that it's innate to animal life, that you're an
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.94,0:15:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.04,0:15:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you stop resisting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.03,0:15:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.03,0:15:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask God to recontextualize it to you so that you see what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.03,0:15:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it an embrace of love and closeness and expressed in the physical manner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.03,0:16:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just desire, craving or lust, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.03,0:16:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is it coming out of the heart or is it coming out of a lower chakra?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.03,0:16:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you try to raise the energy of it as much as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you just see that it's innate to biologic life, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a dominant, like an addiction, that's a different problem, a different problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I would seek like a 12-step program over sexual addiction, that's a different thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you have to ask yourself, is it within the normal range, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.69,0:16:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it ruling your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it causing pain and suffering to yourself or others?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.69,0:16:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an addiction when it's causing pain and suffering to yourself and others, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It also has to do with breathing up some of the energy from the lower chakras to higher
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,chakras.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe some yoga exercises where you picture the energy running up from the lower chakra
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,up through into the heart, let's say, or up into the third eye, you know, or the crown.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do some yoga exercises like that, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see if that's writing or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.67,0:17:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.67,0:17:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Age takes care of it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still obsessed with sex at 90, you better call my office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Doc, I just wanted to say thank you for answering my last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it was your answer or being up here, but I was able to see my issue in
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.70,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,a whole new light, so thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question has to do with the ego and revelation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.70,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I find myself praying for understanding in situations, and sometimes it seems like something
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.20,0:18:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.20,0:18:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it's completely changed and I see it in a whole new light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's recontextualized, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And then within a second, less than a second, the ego comes in and says, well, you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.20,0:18:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,really know anything that isn't valid and negates this very powerful, I don't know if
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.94,0:18:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,answer is the right word, but whatever has just come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do I do about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.94,0:18:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you go back to the reflection and continue to reflect on it until it becomes reconfirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, it becomes reconfirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.70,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And it leaves no doubt in the mind and the ego just sort of backs up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.07,0:19:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You get a certain understanding, then the ego returns and recaps it the way it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you just keep praying and consciously recall the different way you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.58,0:19:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask the Holy Spirit for a miracle to recontextualize it so you can see it again in a different
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.58,0:19:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's true, it'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.34,0:19:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come back as a revelation again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But sometimes they're evanescent in the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.05,0:19:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.05,0:19:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is from the parents of a one-week-old baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.05,0:19:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The baby was born a week ago with advanced leukemia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.24,0:19:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the doctor is doing transfusions and they said that if they keep him for at least
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,a week, he'll recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.90,0:19:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.90,0:19:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,For at least a month, they will give him chemotherapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.90,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But even then, there's not much chance of recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.90,0:20:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So the mother would like to know or...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Should you take heroic measures when they're going to be futile in the end is what you're
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,asking, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.90,0:20:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whether we could ask through kinesiology if the baby, whose name is Trevor, would
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,rather stay in the hospital and be subjected to all the medical treatments or whether he
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.90,0:20:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,would want to go home with the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,A baby isn't going to think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an adult's kind of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.02,0:20:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the mother would like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose that's what...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't imagine that the baby thinks like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the soul, the spirit certainly knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.72,0:20:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul doesn't think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.72,0:20:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the soul is embodied right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.72,0:20:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a thinking body, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a one-week-old infant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.72,0:20:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.72,0:20:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it would be the responsibility of the parents.
