Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.85,0:37:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.85,0:37:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi doctor hi Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.84,0:37:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently I was I was waiting for the results of a test that I had taken
