Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.10,0:37:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A strong feeling and preference
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.10,0:37:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And ask for a specific outcome to occur
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.10,0:38:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Well the only outcome
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.10,0:38:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That I think it makes sense to ask for
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.10,0:38:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is to become aware of God's will in the matter
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.10,0:38:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To ask the Holy Spirit to recontextualize it so that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.10,0:38:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know you see the answer for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.13,0:38:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To reframe it you might say
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.42,0:38:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use the arm and ask you know
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.42,0:38:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way serves the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.16,0:38:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What outcome would serve the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.16,0:38:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You could also surrender trying to control it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.16,0:38:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you don't know what's for the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.16,0:38:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And to not get it could be for the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.16,0:38:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.16,0:38:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So other than using the arm like we do
