Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.44,0:38:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes what you'll get is that
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.44,0:38:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter either way
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Because what counted was your intention in the first place
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.96,0:38:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So which whether you play croquet or tennis
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.96,0:38:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is irrelevant see
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.40,0:38:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And on you know so called deeper or meatier matters
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.40,0:38:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know suppose a loved one was in the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.40,0:39:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Having diagnostic work done to determine whether
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.40,0:39:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know they were going to be around much longer or not
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.40,0:39:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it are we in any way abdicating some responsibility
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.40,0:39:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,As a family member let's say
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.40,0:39:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In not praying for their health
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.40,0:39:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it actually in truly surrendering to God
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.40,0:39:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it best just to say God
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.40,0:39:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord you know what needs to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.40,0:39:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a sin to ask you know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.40,0:39:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,To express your wish in the matter
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.40,0:39:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know you want to pray for the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.60,0:39:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.60,0:39:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So simply to rather than stating a specific preference
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.60,0:39:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Simply to say whatever is in the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.60,0:39:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord that's what my intention is
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.60,0:39:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well trying to specify in spiritual language
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.60,0:39:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Is called outlining
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.60,0:39:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm praying for God's will in this matter
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.04,0:39:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And that I should win you know
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.04,0:39:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Outline is telling God how you want it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.04,0:39:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right and God doesn't need any help from us
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.04,0:40:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well God gets bombarded with advice all day long
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.23,0:40:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What serves the highest good I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.23,0:40:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We always assume that winning
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.23,0:40:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Winning serves the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.23,0:40:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.26,0:40:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But not necessarily so
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.26,0:40:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's certain things you can only learn through defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.26,0:40:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.26,0:40:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore defeat means success to the self with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.26,0:40:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.26,0:40:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's viewed as failure
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.26,0:40:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.26,0:40:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,To the self with a small s
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.26,0:40:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Like the child with leukemia you know
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.26,0:40:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe only a few months of existence this time
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.26,0:40:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.26,0:40:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be for the highest good
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.26,0:40:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But that already served it
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.71,0:40:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it was just paying off a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.71,0:40:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why hang around after you've paid off a lifetime
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.74,0:40:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You already paid that one off
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.74,0:40:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's next
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.74,0:40:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.41,0:41:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the intention
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.12,0:41:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The intensity of your intention
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.12,0:41:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That you ask for God's will in the matter
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.12,0:41:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask for the humility to be grateful and acceptance
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.12,0:41:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the expression of that will whatever it might be
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.12,0:41:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.07,0:41:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.07,0:41:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Susan
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.07,0:41:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.10,0:41:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could help me
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.10,0:41:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious about the origins of the third step prayer in AA
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.10,0:41:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If you knew the origins or the authorship of that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.10,0:41:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it biblically based or did Bill do it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.10,0:41:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of this came from the Oxford groups
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.10,0:41:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.10,0:41:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And Roland had relapsed after he saw Carl Jung
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.10,0:41:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And he went back
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.32,0:41:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Carl Jung said alas and alack
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.32,0:41:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither my science nor my art can help you
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.32,0:41:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But from time to time
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.61,0:41:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,There has been reported of miraculous recoveries
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.61,0:42:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Of people who threw themselves intently into spiritual groups wholeheartedly
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.61,0:42:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roland went back downhearted and discouraged
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.77,0:42:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And he discovered the Oxford groups
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.77,0:42:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Oxford groups I think didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.77,0:42:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of twelve steps I think they only had five or six
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.77,0:42:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But the basic ones of AA
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.77,0:42:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My question was really if the origins of the third step prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.28,0:42:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That they use in Alcoholics Anonymous
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.35,0:42:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.35,0:42:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The prayer of the one that's in chapter five
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.67,0:42:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Where it's God I offer myself to thee to build with me
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.67,0:42:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And do with me as I will
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.67,0:42:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a way of expressing it
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.67,0:42:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Third step is you surrender yourself to God's will
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.67,0:42:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.67,0:42:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering if you knew who might have
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.67,0:42:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Bill write that himself
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.67,0:42:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had any idea about that
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.40,0:42:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that one of the Oxford groups steps
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.30,0:42:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I would imagine it originates from there
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.30,0:42:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just wondering that specific prayer that's in the big book
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.36,0:43:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You know if that was a biblical based thing or
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.36,0:43:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.36,0:43:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,All I know is that it originated primarily from the Oxford groups
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.36,0:43:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it was tailored for application to alcoholism
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.36,0:43:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was curious because you know we use
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.36,0:43:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We use the prayer of Saint Francis
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.36,0:43:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.36,0:43:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In AA but I've never heard it said
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.36,0:43:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who actually wrote that short third step prayer
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.36,0:43:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.36,0:43:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't give you the historical background on it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.36,0:43:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.36,0:43:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.01,0:43:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The third step is really intrinsic to all high spiritual teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.01,0:43:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Throughout history no matter who it is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.01,0:43:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it's the Buddha or Krishna
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.11,0:43:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She painted it
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.11,0:43:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh wow
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.11,0:44:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so many talented people here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.39,0:44:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.39,0:44:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.86,0:44:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back to the question of the soul
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.86,0:44:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul and the highest self
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.86,0:44:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are the same thing, is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.86,0:44:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Higher what?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.86,0:44:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The soul and the higher self are the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.86,0:44:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.86,0:44:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the soul has
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.86,0:44:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of people do this type of work
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.86,0:44:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And they say things like well I had to learn that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.86,0:44:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And my argument is that the soul doesn't have to learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.08,0:44:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.08,0:44:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The capitalist soul self doesn't have to learn anything
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.08,0:44:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.08,0:44:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But the smalls?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.08,0:44:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But the smalls
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.08,0:44:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The small self
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.08,0:44:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.08,0:44:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Has to learn a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.08,0:44:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The small self which is the ego?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.08,0:44:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.08,0:44:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.08,0:44:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What does the ego have to learn?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.20,0:44:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,No I'm serious because I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.32,0:45:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to learn humility, reverence for God
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.32,0:45:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that just be surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.32,0:45:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender of willfulness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.32,0:45:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.32,0:45:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just surrender?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.32,0:45:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to surrender its self-servingness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.15,0:45:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Its own selfishness
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.15,0:45:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.15,0:45:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And its alignment with the linear and
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.15,0:45:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To align with the non-linear dimension
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.15,0:45:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.15,0:45:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.01,0:45:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.01,0:45:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.01,0:45:32.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Through devotion, selfless service, devotion
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.01,0:45:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodwill towards all of life
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.11,0:45:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The willingness to be loving no matter what
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.24,0:45:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't though come from the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.24,0:45:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that come from the higher self?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.36,0:45:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes well I'm telling you how to overcome the lower self yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.36,0:45:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.36,0:45:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.55,0:45:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When the change occurs
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.55,0:45:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's quite obvious what the ego, small ego was
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.55,0:45:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.00,0:45:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.96,0:45:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you still confused?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.96,0:46:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Well that's okay I'll work on it and see you next year
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.24,0:46:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're a little
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.08,0:46:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Your intention will carry you through don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.08,0:46:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.08,0:46:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very complex subject when you tack it first in your mind you know
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.14,0:46:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well see I teach a course in miracles at home
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.14,0:46:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And my argument that I make to the people
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.14,0:46:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They will say oh I had to learn that I had to learn that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.14,0:46:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh oh
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.14,0:46:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And what I say to them is that what's really important
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.14,0:46:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that you remember who you are
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.14,0:46:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where you put your focus
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.14,0:46:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can remember who you or what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.14,0:46:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can remember what you are
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.14,0:46:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that sort of just takes care of all that other stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.14,0:46:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That the ego likes to think you have to learn and figure out
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.14,0:46:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a shortcut yes
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.61,0:47:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It gains momentum with familiarity
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.40,0:47:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So the more I say that the more people will be able to
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.20,0:47:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.20,0:47:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.20,0:47:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Realize the truth of it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.20,0:47:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't have to tell anybody anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.45,0:47:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You just be that to them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.45,0:47:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Instructions are good in the beginning
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.31,0:47:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After a while they dissolve into the way you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.31,0:47:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.37,0:47:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I got that one
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.37,0:47:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.37,0:47:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.11,0:47:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.11,0:47:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become the student
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.11,0:47:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not studying out of your students
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.11,0:47:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the student
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.11,0:47:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore you bring forth answers to your questions
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.11,0:47:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.11,0:47:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about hot flashes can you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.11,0:47:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't do anything about hot flashes can you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.78,0:47:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm having one you couldn't do anything about them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.78,0:47:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your suggestion
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.78,0:47:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Fifty percent of the women out there need help
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.78,0:48:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a million cures for hot flashes out there
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.78,0:48:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't found one
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.78,0:48:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh you haven't looked hard enough
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.78,0:48:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of good answers to hot flashes
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.13,0:48:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You got just one good one
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.16,0:48:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd have to sit down in a session you see
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.16,0:48:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.16,0:48:19.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay because it's partly a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.16,0:48:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is physical mental and spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a belief system
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.16,0:48:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So you do what hormonally you have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.16,0:48:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You do what physically you have to do
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.16,0:48:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You let go in the belief system that you're subject to them
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.16,0:48:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you pray at the same time
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.16,0:48:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you're doing physical mental and spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.16,0:48:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest is just a matter of patience
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.16,0:48:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.60,0:48:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I like that
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.60,0:48:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get old and gray they'll be gone
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.44,0:48:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.44,0:48:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.56,0:49:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I really don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.32,0:49:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been coming to your lectures for quite a while
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.32,0:49:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to express
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.32,0:49:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That you've been such a wonderful part of my journey
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.39,0:49:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.39,0:49:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.39,0:49:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.39,0:49:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And just express my gratitude
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.39,0:49:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.39,0:49:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.39,0:49:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I had many questions along the time
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.87,0:49:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Never had enough guts to get up here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.87,0:49:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But interestingly enough I noticed that eventually
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.87,0:49:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They just lost their importance
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.03,0:49:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes that's what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.03,0:49:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's awesome
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.03,0:49:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,As you go to talk to the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.03,0:49:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly they dissolve
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.03,0:49:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And you realize it isn't a problem
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.03,0:49:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And that was the answer you were seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.19,0:49:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.19,0:49:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I just wanted to be here closer to you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.50,0:49:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.50,0:49:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.50,0:49:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.77,0:50:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.77,0:50:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.77,0:50:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I work with people in the context of psychotherapy and healing and so forth
Dialogue: 0,0:50:06.80,0:50:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So I have my theoretical orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.80,0:50:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Psychology and spirituality
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.80,0:50:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel very much drawn to this
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.80,0:50:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And coming here as well
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.80,0:50:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But they don't 100% kind of match
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.80,0:50:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially with calibrations sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.80,0:50:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What I think might help is
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.80,0:50:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd be willing to calibrate the work that I do
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.80,0:50:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,With people
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.80,0:50:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.44,0:50:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.44,0:50:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We could
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.44,0:50:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're talking about multi-faceted
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.44,0:50:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So what facet are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.44,0:50:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, oh, hmm, I don't know
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.73,0:50:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean can't you just do it as a whole?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.73,0:50:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,As a hole in the wall?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.50,0:50:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it as a hole in the wall
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.11,0:50:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're calibrated so we're 20
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.14,0:50:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to ask permission
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.14,0:50:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.14,0:50:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I give permission
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.14,0:50:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.14,0:50:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're calibrated so we're 20
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.14,0:51:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're 200
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.14,0:51:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's important
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.14,0:51:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.14,0:51:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.14,0:51:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.14,0:51:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So right
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.14,0:51:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't calibrate myself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.14,0:51:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of that I just don't care
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.14,0:51:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still had wanted to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.14,0:51:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I see what you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.14,0:51:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.14,0:51:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well it's not an academic approach
Dialogue: 0,0:51:12.14,0:51:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:51:13.14,0:51:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a clinical approach
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.14,0:51:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.14,0:51:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So what you want is something probably in the high 300s around there
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.14,0:51:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.14,0:51:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.24,0:51:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what's academic?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.24,0:51:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I missed that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.24,0:51:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your approach to patients academic?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.24,0:51:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's primarily spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.24,0:51:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I present myself
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.24,0:51:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's clinical and spiritual
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.24,0:51:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.24,0:51:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.24,0:51:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I mean I use the Jungian stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.24,0:51:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's eclectic I dare say
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.24,0:51:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Composite
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.24,0:51:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Using the dirty word
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.24,0:51:38.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.24,0:51:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that
Dialogue: 0,0:51:39.24,0:51:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:40.24,0:51:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words it's not strict medical, medical practice
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.24,0:51:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I call
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.24,0:51:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the 400s
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.24,0:51:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I call it consciousness psychotherapy
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.24,0:51:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.24,0:51:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I pick that because that's my sense is really whatever they're coming for and however we work
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.24,0:51:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't create some greater awareness
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.24,0:51:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.24,0:51:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just moving things around
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.24,0:51:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.24,0:51:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not really doing a permanent
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.24,0:52:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're trying to recontextualize things
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.24,0:52:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.24,0:52:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.24,0:52:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.24,0:52:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.24,0:52:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's very good, very good
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.24,0:52:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's sophisticated
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.24,0:52:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.24,0:52:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.24,0:52:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.15,0:52:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What counts is that it's over 200
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.15,0:52:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.15,0:52:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.08,0:52:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.08,0:52:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's integrous, so
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.17,0:52:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a wide latitude
Dialogue: 0,0:52:23.17,0:52:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.17,0:52:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beautiful
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.60,0:52:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd given it to you for once now
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.60,0:52:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's gorgeous
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.60,0:52:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's actually
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.60,0:52:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most precious thing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.60,0:52:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.60,0:52:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So it goes to you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.60,0:52:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.60,0:52:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Docs
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.60,0:52:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you again
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.46,0:52:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.46,0:52:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you both very much
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.65,0:52:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm very grateful to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.65,0:52:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in the area two weeks
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.65,0:52:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been pretty amazing
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.72,0:52:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I moved here from Maui
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.72,0:52:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.72,0:52:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I left
Dialogue: 0,0:52:56.72,0:52:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So if you guys are still gonna go
Dialogue: 0,0:52:57.72,0:52:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I know people there
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.72,0:52:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nice condos on the beach
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.72,0:53:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.09,0:53:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with intention and karma
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.35,0:53:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of the mindset of, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.66,0:53:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you intend
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.66,0:53:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And hold it in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.66,0:53:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.66,0:53:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And it seems like to a certain point
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.66,0:53:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.04,0:53:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, it's like
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.04,0:53:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been holding certain things in mind for years
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.04,0:53:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And, you know, it just seems like
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.11,0:53:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a karmic thing
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.11,0:53:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it hasn't come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.11,0:53:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not gonna come
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.11,0:53:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I'm just not waiting long enough
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.56,0:53:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:53:35.56,0:53:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, what's the relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.65,0:53:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I've watched the intention video several times
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.65,0:53:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I, you know, I'm pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.65,0:53:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to make something happen with intention
Dialogue: 0,0:53:45.65,0:53:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.65,0:53:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to control it
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.07,0:53:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're complaining that it hasn't happened
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.10,0:53:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore you're trying to control it and make it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.10,0:53:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let go of wanting to make it happen
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.13,0:53:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention is not a tool
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.13,0:54:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,To try to force karmic
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.71,0:54:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Cosmic forces, you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.71,0:54:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention is only an influence
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.71,0:54:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a contextual field
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.71,0:54:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Then within that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.71,0:54:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Propensities will manifest or not manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.80,0:54:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're responsible for the effort
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.80,0:54:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But not the result
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.80,0:54:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.80,0:54:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.80,0:54:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.80,0:54:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So whatever the result is, it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.80,0:54:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.80,0:54:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,For it not to happen, that's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.80,0:54:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.80,0:54:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It could be the death of you
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.83,0:54:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I've already said
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.83,0:54:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh Lord, let me be present
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.83,0:54:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, assassination
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.83,0:54:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you God
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.83,0:54:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.83,0:54:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets rid of that one
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.83,0:54:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's
Dialogue: 0,0:54:40.47,0:54:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess the
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.47,0:54:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there's a lot of the intentionality stuff around abundance and this
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.47,0:54:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Around what?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.47,0:54:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Abundance
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.47,0:54:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.47,0:54:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you good?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.47,0:54:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hold this and that and that
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.47,0:54:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm not attached to the abundance thing
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.47,0:55:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wouldn't mind having a little improvement
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.40,0:55:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a job right now would be great
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.61,0:55:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because I want to, you know, live up to my responsibilities
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.61,0:55:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which are still my debts
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.61,0:55:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you frustrated about?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.61,0:55:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.09,0:55:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.09,0:55:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, I'd like a job
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.09,0:55:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm almost there
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.09,0:55:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the newspaper here has about six pages of jobs
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.09,0:55:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, every day
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.09,0:55:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk down any street and have a job within ten minutes flat
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.09,0:55:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So not having a job is not really something you need to pray about
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.09,0:55:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Just need something to go get
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.09,0:55:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.09,0:55:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that will come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.09,0:55:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One will come that will suffice
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.09,0:55:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, when you walk around the corner
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.09,0:55:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta walk around the corner to get a job
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.09,0:55:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been driving all over to get a job
Dialogue: 0,0:55:35.09,0:55:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single store in Sedona has a sign of wanting
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.09,0:55:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.09,0:55:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So how can you not get a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.09,0:55:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It must take some real
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.09,0:55:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.09,0:55:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Adopt for this
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.09,0:55:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm looking
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.09,0:55:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm, I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.09,0:55:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's
Dialogue: 0,0:55:46.09,0:55:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want just any job
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.09,0:55:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, any job
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.09,0:55:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want a job that's gonna provide for me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.09,0:55:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a job that's gonna provide for me
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.09,0:55:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.09,0:55:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, the job will come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.09,0:55:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.09,0:55:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll come
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.09,0:55:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, so that's not really the problem
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.09,0:55:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm just trying to
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.09,0:56:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Something more long-term you've been holding in mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.09,0:56:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I guess it's
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.99,0:56:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to understand the, the role that karma plays in intention
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.56,0:56:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If one holds an intention, does that intention come about because of your karma?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:15.56,0:56:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of the karmic pattern that you hold
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.60,0:56:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it won't manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.60,0:56:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's some karmic blockage
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.60,0:56:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it won't manifest
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.60,0:56:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.60,0:56:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, okay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.48,0:56:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, basically
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.48,0:56:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you're responsible for the effort, not the result
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.48,0:56:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:56:28.48,0:56:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still trying to control the result
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.48,0:56:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.48,0:56:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what you're telling me over and over
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.48,0:56:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been doing this and what I wanted hasn't happened yet
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.48,0:56:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.48,0:56:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I'm still attached to the outcome
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.48,0:56:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give up what it is you want to happen
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.48,0:56:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And just use a decent amount of effort and what comes up, comes up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.48,0:56:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, it's let go of the attachment to the outcome
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.48,0:56:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.48,0:56:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.48,0:56:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.48,0:56:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.48,0:56:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just holding it up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.48,0:56:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.48,0:56:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.48,0:56:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:45.71,0:56:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.71,0:56:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.71,0:56:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.71,0:56:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.71,0:56:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.71,0:56:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.71,0:56:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.71,0:56:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.71,0:56:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.71,0:56:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, pretty much
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.77,0:56:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What I hold in mind or intend is oneness with God
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.77,0:57:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And, and then other things in the world, you know, things you'd like, like maybe your
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.13,0:57:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.13,0:57:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, why don't you just hold your your happiness in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.13,0:57:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And then whatever it takes to make you happy
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.13,0:57:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll follow them
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.13,0:57:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead of trying to outline how that happiness should come about
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.41,0:57:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain salary
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.41,0:57:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain location
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.41,0:57:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.41,0:57:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain car
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.41,0:57:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,A certain person
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.37,0:57:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was God, I'd just get fatigued, you know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.37,0:57:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.37,0:57:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be happy or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.79,0:57:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I want to be happy
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.79,0:57:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just hold that in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.27,0:57:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just hold thatonia
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.21,0:57:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,just hold that
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.05,0:57:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that you feel satisfied, fulfilled, and happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.13,0:57:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Without even, like, well, without visualizing, without...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.75,0:57:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualizing is adding another true sense worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.57,0:57:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not going to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.71,0:57:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but you talked about visualizing on that lit.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.15,0:57:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.09,0:57:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's, I'm not understanding that.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.05,0:57:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualize happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.05,0:57:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, potentiality, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.07,0:57:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Visualizing increases the potentiality of a likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.79,0:57:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.43,0:57:53.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.45,0:57:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.35,0:57:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Holding a certain thing in mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.13,0:58:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,tends to statistically increase the likelihood of that happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.95,0:58:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't control it, because it's still non...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.25,0:58:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of the right mathematical term.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.28,0:58:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not non-deterministic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.96,0:58:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking at prayer and intention, all that is deterministic.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.32,0:58:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're influencing is likelihoods.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.56,0:58:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're increasing the likelihood of a certain realm manifesting,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.12,0:58:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're not going to control it or make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.66,0:58:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be more general.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.51,0:58:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you're being too specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.03,0:58:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you picture yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.31,0:58:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Being satisfied, happy, and fulfilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.25,0:58:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,And then let God fill in how that's to come about,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.53,0:58:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,because you obviously don't know, or you wouldn't be complaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.11,0:58:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.69,0:58:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.43,0:58:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.45,0:58:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.85,0:58:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, so just basically visualize happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.14,0:58:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There, feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.82,0:58:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want for your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.76,0:58:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, don't you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.70,0:59:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's always been a hard thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.58,0:59:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know that you want to be happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.94,0:59:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.42,0:59:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.36,0:59:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.04,0:59:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I want to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.50,0:59:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know I want to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.64,0:59:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.22,0:59:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't made that point at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.58,0:59:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.36,0:59:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.08,0:59:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you getting at?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.00,0:59:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I want this, this, and this to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.50,0:59:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's like...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.86,0:59:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're outlining.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.34,0:59:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's kind of that thing like you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.18,0:59:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,if I get this, then I'll be happy kind of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.34,0:59:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.54,0:59:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.06,0:59:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to elevate your level of consciousness and the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.58,0:59:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And be...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.58,0:59:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go for the generic happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.38,0:59:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You ask God, you want to fulfill God's will for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.22,0:59:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.16,0:59:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ask God for your knowledge of his will for me and the power to carry it out, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.12,0:59:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And to fulfill my potential and to serve God and myself and mankind all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.14,0:59:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The power to carry it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.84,0:59:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And then go out and around the corner and get a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.50,0:59:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring broccoli.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.70,0:59:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to bring broccoli to the next lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.56,1:00:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What does broccoli say all the time, Susie?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.66,1:00:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to work.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.22,1:00:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Get a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.04,1:00:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.94,1:00:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There is one right around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.46,1:00:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.54,1:00:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.32,1:00:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.30,1:00:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.60,1:00:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,One time I took a job.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.04,1:00:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I used to have trouble.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.52,1:00:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In the summertime, I'd have to find a short-term job, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.70,1:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And by fall, they had me in executive training for 20th Century Fox.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.60,1:00:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was looking for a summer job.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.23,1:00:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully, that'll be the case for me soon.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.21,1:00:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.89,1:00:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.89,1:00:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.31,1:00:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.99,1:00:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I started out as an usher, so you don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.97,1:00:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You would be saying, oh, I don't want to work as an usher.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.45,1:00:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,But by the end of the summer, I was in executive training for 20th Century Fox.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.54,1:00:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We sold more buttered popcorn than any theater in the chain.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.14,1:00:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.34,1:01:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today has been fabulous.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.04,1:01:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is also on intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.04,1:01:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I experienced about three weeks ago, I was a little bit late to work,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:09.34,1:01:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have quite a long commute.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.04,1:01:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And as I was driving, it just came to me to put out an intention that I'm there on time, safe,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.26,1:01:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and without any interference, because a lot of times there's trucks.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:21.10,1:01:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got, it's an hour and 15 minutes to work,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.82,1:01:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so I got to a place where all of a sudden the cars were backed up.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.96,1:01:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And at that moment, there was an old farm road to the right.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.94,1:01:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I just took it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.02,1:01:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea where it was going.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.44,1:01:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I followed it, and I came around a corner,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.80,1:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and there were a lot of other cars.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.84,1:01:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And there was a wave to me from the school where I was,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.24,1:01:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and I just followed it in.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.30,1:01:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,There were fatalities in the accident,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.30,1:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the clerks was calling all the rooms
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.30,1:01:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure the teachers were there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.30,1:01:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I said, you won't believe this,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.30,1:01:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but I put out an intention, not knowing there was an accident,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.30,1:01:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and all these things happened.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.30,1:02:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she said, Sue,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.30,1:02:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I prayed this morning that I would see God at work somewhere on this campus,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.30,1:02:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's already happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:07.30,1:02:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realized that intentionality,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:09.30,1:02:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,intentionality, intentionality, intentionality, intentionality, intentionality, intentionality, intentionality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.22,1:02:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.22,1:02:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In that moment, it seemed that I didn't have that intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.22,1:02:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,that there was some power.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:18.22,1:02:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,When we do have an intention,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.22,1:02:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is it ours or is it Spirit with a capital S leading us to our next greater good,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.22,1:02:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,knowing where that is?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.22,1:02:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.92,1:02:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So over 200 when we have the etheric brain,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.12,1:02:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't, it's just accept whatever comes?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.12,1:02:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:40.12,1:02:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.63,1:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's automatically going to align with the higher power field.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.63,1:02:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.63,1:02:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And if it's permissible to happen,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.63,1:02:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the likelihood will increase that it happens.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.63,1:02:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's not permissible,
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.63,1:02:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,then it won't have any effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.63,1:02:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.98,1:03:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not having it happen is okay, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.98,1:03:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.98,1:03:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.98,1:03:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that would be, I just had never,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.98,1:03:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it just came to me, this stunning beauty of this moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.98,1:03:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that I could not have accounted for.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.98,1:03:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the intention, the likelihood?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.98,1:03:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's mathematically so, also, quantum mechanics.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.98,1:03:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.75,1:03:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Next lecture we have is on, is the miraculous real.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:23.84,1:03:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In November?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.84,1:03:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the next one.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.84,1:03:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,December.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:27.84,1:03:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in December.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.84,1:03:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not coming to that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.84,1:03:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming to November.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.84,1:03:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't have a miracle then.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.84,1:03:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Until next year.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:36.84,1:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be back for the miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.84,1:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.84,1:03:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You already had a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.84,1:03:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I have miracles every day.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.84,1:03:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, miracles, see, people don't recognize them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.84,1:03:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's for the miraculous,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.84,1:03:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,where your intention brings about the manifestation
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.84,1:03:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,of a different likelihood.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.84,1:03:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was stunning for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.13,1:03:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment was stunning.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.13,1:03:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I just, I was in awe, because when I was praying,
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.58,1:03:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it was, just get me to daub on time.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.58,1:04:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:00.58,1:04:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.58,1:04:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And this was special.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.58,1:04:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.58,1:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.74,1:04:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Great.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.74,1:04:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.40,1:04:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've struggled with a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.40,1:04:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I've struggled with a lot of recurrent depression
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.40,1:04:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and anxiety throughout this life.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.40,1:04:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've successfully treated the symptoms of it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.40,1:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,on physical and mental levels.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.40,1:04:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.40,1:04:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm wondering, in order to resolve it,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.11,1:04:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,do I need to, is it necessary to get to a karmic origin
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.11,1:04:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of it in some specific way?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.11,1:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It may, I'm not talking about, now karma is like,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.11,1:04:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,an experience that reduplicates,
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.11,1:04:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a different kind.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.11,1:05:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Karmically, you could say the evolution
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.59,1:05:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of your consciousness is such that it gets tripped up
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.59,1:05:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,at certain points for reasons you don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.59,1:05:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But you ask God, you know, to reveal to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.59,1:05:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, what, is there a greater meaning to this
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.59,1:05:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,than I'm supposed to be seeing?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:14.88,1:05:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And then it either reveals itself or it doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.88,1:05:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,See, there's no timing in these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.05,1:05:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to be depressed for eight or ten years.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.05,1:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Suddenly it goes away.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.05,1:05:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And in that same instant that it goes away,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.05,1:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,you also get the karmic experience of it,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.21,1:05:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,the karmic background of it, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.72,1:05:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't tell because it isn't a linear sequence
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.72,1:05:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,that makes sense necessarily.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.72,1:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, you might be 60 years old,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.16,1:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and one day you're sitting out in the hammock
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.16,1:05:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden you say,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.16,1:05:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,oh, God, I see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.16,1:05:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.08,1:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mysterious in a way.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.36,1:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The non-linear, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.59,1:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The linear mind tries to make sense of the non-linear,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.59,1:06:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.59,1:06:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Retrospectively, you can say,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.51,1:06:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,aha, but anticipatorily,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.67,1:06:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't really predict it.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.67,1:06:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't unravel in any kind of predictable, logical way.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.67,1:06:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.88,1:06:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:29.89,1:06:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you got rid of the symptoms,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.89,1:06:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's sane and logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:35.02,1:06:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.69,1:06:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.75,1:06:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.84,1:06:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you, I'm compelled to tell you
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.91,1:06:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,just how giddy I am
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.91,1:06:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,about this because I was so excited
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.91,1:06:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,when I first read your first book.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.91,1:06:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I was like, I mean,
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.71,1:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,although I had to have a dictionary on one side
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.71,1:06:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and the book on the other.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:01.71,1:07:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're smart.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.71,1:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have changed my life profoundly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.71,1:07:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I mean, it's been so exciting.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.71,1:07:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, and speaking of surrendering
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.71,1:07:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and such like that,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.71,1:07:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have worked very hard on those and it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.71,1:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, I don't have no stress.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:19.71,1:07:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I have, I mean, I will live my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.71,1:07:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm just, my family thinks I'm .
Dialogue: 0,1:07:27.71,1:07:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.71,1:07:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Flippy doodle, eh?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.71,1:07:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.71,1:07:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But I wanted to tell you how much,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.84,1:07:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what an impact you've had on me.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.84,1:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, you coming back from your journey
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.22,1:07:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and bringing with you all this insight
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.22,1:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and all this valuable information
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.22,1:07:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is just unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.22,1:07:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, I.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.22,1:07:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If I've got just another second,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.22,1:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how I heard about you,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.22,1:07:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,because I want to,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.22,1:07:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to give,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.22,1:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,let the audience hear how I really,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:55.22,1:07:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but I happened to be mowing the lawn.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.22,1:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I came in the house and there was Wayne Dyer on TV.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.22,1:08:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And the only thing I heard out of his mouth was,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.22,1:08:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,we all have an appointment with infinity.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.22,1:08:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't we all?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.21,1:08:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And he says,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.50,1:08:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,why don't you make an appointment with infinity today?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.50,1:08:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm telling you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:16.33,1:08:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,So instead of being stressful and dying,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.33,1:08:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I was just going to make an appointment
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.33,1:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,with infinity today and surrender all that stuff
Dialogue: 0,1:08:25.33,1:08:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,and then just be,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.33,1:08:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,just enjoy my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.33,1:08:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.33,1:08:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, just go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.33,1:08:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go with the flow.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.33,1:08:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Zingo.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:31.43,1:08:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I hope you can see the excitement in me
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.43,1:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.43,1:08:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And you just go on your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:45.20,1:08:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.10,1:08:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.10,1:08:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.10,1:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.76,1:08:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And you get the spiritual.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.76,1:08:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get the spiritual wheel going,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.76,1:08:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't really go.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.80,1:09:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a tough act to follow.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:04.80,1:09:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.80,1:09:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Hawkins, for everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.80,1:09:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is coming from the eight-year-old
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.80,1:09:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that lives inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.80,1:09:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very trivial compared to everybody else's question.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.80,1:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm wondering,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:16.80,1:09:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when you first moved to Sedona,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.80,1:09:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you calibrated it, I'm sure, the energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.80,1:09:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And has it changed?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.80,1:09:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.31,1:09:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.31,1:09:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.31,1:09:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.31,1:09:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.31,1:09:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.31,1:09:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.31,1:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody ever asked me to.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.47,1:09:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody asked you to?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.47,1:09:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.47,1:09:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.47,1:09:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think it's changed?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.47,1:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.47,1:09:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here seven years.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.47,1:09:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I see a lot of changes,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.47,1:09:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't feel the energy shifting that much.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.47,1:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.47,1:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And maybe it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.47,1:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe it hasn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.47,1:09:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's even pertinent.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.47,1:09:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,We have permission to ask about Sedona.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:45.47,1:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.47,1:09:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,My eight-year-old child is very disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.47,1:09:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because you're a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.47,1:09:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:49.47,1:09:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.79,1:09:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.79,1:09:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.79,1:09:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.79,1:09:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.79,1:09:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a child.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.79,1:09:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very disappointed.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.79,1:09:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's because spiritual groups
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.79,1:09:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have such a powerful energy
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.79,1:09:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.79,1:10:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.79,1:10:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you'd have to differentiate, you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.79,1:10:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.79,1:10:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a group that's aligned with enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.79,1:10:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.79,1:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very powerful group.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.79,1:10:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.79,1:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So, would you include them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.79,1:10:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as part or parcel of,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:08.79,1:10:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,are they residents of your,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.79,1:10:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.79,1:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,so you,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.79,1:10:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how we'd diagnose it,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.79,1:10:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.79,1:10:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.79,1:10:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.79,1:10:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a place that is charitable
Dialogue: 0,1:10:16.79,1:10:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to spiritually oriented people.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.79,1:10:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:18.79,1:10:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.79,1:10:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
