Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.83,1:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,medication is some pain medications are addictive have an addictive potential
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.81,1:12:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and others don't if you're sick with ibuprofen aspirin things like that they
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.07,1:12:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,have no addictive propensity if you get into coding the addict and you could get
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.79,1:12:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to like in the coding yes so you could try acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.59,1:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture acupuncture is excellent for things like that great and so
Dialogue: 0,1:12:33.45,1:12:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,acupuncture plus non-addictive pain relievers self-hypnosis is a variety I
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.63,1:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,was that I had good experience with acupuncture frankly with a variety of
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.53,1:12:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,pretty bad ones too okay thank you he had a collapse vertebrae so I mean that's
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.78,1:12:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all I had a number of illnesses they responded very well I can puncture so
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.34,1:12:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just telling you that it's safe so non-addictive analgesics plus acupuncture
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.90,1:13:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe self hypnosis there's a variety of techniques you know okay thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.74,1:13:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,alternate alternative medicine yeah okay thank you very much herbs alternative
Dialogue: 0,1:13:21.98,1:13:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,medicine I just have a question regarding spirituality and love for a
Dialogue: 0,1:13:33.88,1:13:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,woman and kids does it get is it is it possible to get to a point where you can
Dialogue: 0,1:13:41.39,1:13:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot love a woman, have a family, to pursue your own spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.90,1:13:51.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing him.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:51.90,1:13:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's asking about love of a woman. Is it possible to get to a point where you don't?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.90,1:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot love a woman and be spiritual at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.90,1:14:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, they're not antithetical at all.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.90,1:14:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love, the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.19,1:14:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you love God, you love your fellow beings, you love life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.19,1:14:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you love, the more you can love.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.35,1:14:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The more you can love, the more you do love.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:18.35,1:14:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The more conditional it becomes.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.54,1:14:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So loving that starts life in all of its expressions is the way you end up, by removing the blocks to life.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.31,1:14:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, then I guess the second part would be why all of the avatars were not married, for example.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:35.31,1:14:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Like Christ and Buddha and so on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.31,1:14:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they didn't like women.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.31,1:14:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.37,1:14:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They were born, don't forget, in different eras.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.37,1:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,And also different parts of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.56,1:15:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So the spiritual tradition of the spiritual teacher is one thing in India, it's another thing in Buddhism, it's another thing in the Hebrew culture.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.56,1:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But Jesus Christ was born incarnated, you know, was already, the presence of divinity was very strong at a very young age, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:09.76,1:15:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And so why each one occurred in that way is hard to say.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.76,1:15:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It would take some research, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:22.00,1:15:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd need half an hour and some meditative time to ask the reason for that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.03,1:15:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.57,1:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,They were the only volunteers around, maybe, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.57,1:15:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody else said, what?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.86,1:15:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come into life and not get married and have kids?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.86,1:15:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The heck with that.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.86,1:15:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.05,1:15:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.05,1:15:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for the first time.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.60,1:16:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I came because I had friends who had been here and I've heard about you and I looked at some books.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.30,1:16:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I read one completely.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.30,1:16:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked at a tape and I listened to an audio cassette.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.22,1:16:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But I had no idea what the presence of the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.82,1:16:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I have three points.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.89,1:17:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There's blue in two of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.08,1:17:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:03.91,1:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.34,1:17:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You can laugh if you like.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.37,1:17:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:11.36,1:17:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But that the presence of the teacher would bring.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:14.36,1:17:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your potential.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.01,1:17:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.01,1:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,First to realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.01,1:17:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:23.01,1:17:46.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That all is as well.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.14,1:17:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a peace that passes the understanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.14,1:17:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't have to know why.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.29,1:17:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And when the mind clears up.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:56.29,1:18:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's able to think clearly.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.90,1:18:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.74,1:18:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't think right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:15.92,1:18:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.92,1:18:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's thinking but he can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.92,1:18:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.92,1:18:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just when the mind clear, thinks clearly, it is such a joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.88,1:18:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To do one thing and then the next and then the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.46,1:18:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And to have the timelessness.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:33.46,1:18:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You wish every human could feel that at least.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.77,1:18:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And the last gift was that it's.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.86,1:18:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That one could die and it's perfectly okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.86,1:19:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't want to die in the last month without coming back and saying thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.38,1:19:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It isn't dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.45,1:19:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's leaving the ego to the old self.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.45,1:19:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.55,1:19:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.55,1:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not dying.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.55,1:19:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being reborn.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.55,1:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.55,1:19:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.55,1:19:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have to grieve it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.55,1:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.55,1:19:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And it.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.55,1:19:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's place is something of greater dimension, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.22,1:19:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.02,1:19:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And with it comes joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.02,1:19:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And an overwhelming joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.02,1:19:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes people lose control.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.02,1:19:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.28,1:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes people can't stop crying for months.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.28,1:19:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.53,1:19:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hard to think about it without getting emotional.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.53,1:19:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think this would happen because I thought I had cried enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.27,1:19:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's common in monasteries.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.27,1:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kind of common in spiritual communities.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.75,1:19:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes people cry for a couple of years.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.75,1:19:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.28,1:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.28,1:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You can cry for 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.28,1:20:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But tears of joy.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:04.69,1:20:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.69,1:20:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.69,1:20:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.69,1:20:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual, the saints tell you that they went through periods where they cried for
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.69,1:20:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,some years.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.69,1:20:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And then in spiritual communities it's common.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:10.69,1:20:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.69,1:20:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And I remember going through the phase.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.69,1:20:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be in an airport.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.98,1:20:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And a couple would be sitting there waiting for a plane.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.98,1:20:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And they would look at each other.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.98,1:20:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got the love.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.98,1:20:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would begin to cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.98,1:20:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Any exposure to love I would cry.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.20,1:20:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A mother with her puppy, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:20.20,1:20:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.20,1:20:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And any kind of expression of love.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.20,1:20:23.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.20,1:20:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would start to cry.
