Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.36,1:21:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes perfect sense
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.04,1:21:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,it falls into place
Dialogue: 0,1:21:24.94,1:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are no words to thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.89,1:21:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,very good you just did
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.17,1:22:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do you have a question?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:00.34,1:22:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea what it was
Dialogue: 0,1:22:02.24,1:22:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,a long time ago
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.86,1:22:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,one lady asked what do you do
Dialogue: 0,1:22:18.70,1:22:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and you said get a box of Kleenex
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.02,1:22:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have some if I didn't spill coffee
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.58,1:22:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,in my car
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.28,1:22:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,let me see if I can remember
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.84,1:22:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the question
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.48,1:22:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,in the picture too
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.86,1:22:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,in the process
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.96,1:22:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,of surrendering
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.95,1:22:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,all things
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.38,1:22:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to God's will
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.48,1:23:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,my life has changed
Dialogue: 0,1:23:06.03,1:23:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in great measure
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.19,1:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of things have been surrendered
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.55,1:23:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,but in that process
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.87,1:23:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,very linear decisions come up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.73,1:23:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.62,1:23:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I surrender the decisions
Dialogue: 0,1:23:19.82,1:23:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,as completely as possible
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.50,1:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and want
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.04,1:23:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,divine will
Dialogue: 0,1:23:25.74,1:23:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,above all else
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.56,1:23:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and I try to use self-kinesiology
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.48,1:23:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't get accurate responses
Dialogue: 0,1:23:32.64,1:23:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've tried using other people
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.34,1:23:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the answer that we usually get is that
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.48,1:23:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,karmically I have to figure it out for myself
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.80,1:23:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.84,1:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you're on your own baby
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.90,1:23:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.82,1:23:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that's tough
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.52,1:23:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and so I guess my question is about discernment
Dialogue: 0,1:23:49.54,1:23:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you know
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.22,1:23:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,when what you feel in your gut
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.07,1:23:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is for the highest good
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.55,1:23:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to worry about
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.85,1:24:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,being the highest good all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.45,1:24:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that's only a way of phrasing the question
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.55,1:24:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,don't worry about it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.28,1:24:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,you see
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.94,1:24:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual commitment already takes care of it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.17,1:24:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,if you say to God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.34,1:24:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I trust in your guidance
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.74,1:24:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and I ask for the expression of your will
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.12,1:24:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to the best of my capacity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.04,1:24:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.68,1:24:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and then let it go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.22,1:24:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,it's his problem
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.08,1:24:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what God's sort of there for
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.88,1:24:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,don't blow your stuff on me
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.46,1:24:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.18,1:24:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry about that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.52,1:24:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.48,1:24:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.24,1:24:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you see you do the best thing you can
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.26,1:24:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you let go of it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.40,1:24:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,that's all
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.46,1:24:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I said to a guy one time
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.00,1:24:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I said look either we blow up or we don't
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.80,1:24:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says you're right
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.12,1:24:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I took care of it
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.50,1:24:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we didn't worry about it after that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.38,1:24:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.30,1:24:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you let go of it in an instant
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.36,1:24:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you say either it's going to be that way or not that way
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.26,1:24:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in that instant you surrender it to God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.10,1:25:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you forget about it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.44,1:25:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever happens is whatever happens
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.82,1:25:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.50,1:25:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.04,1:25:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.80,1:25:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you say dear God thank you for showing me
Dialogue: 0,1:25:14.84,1:25:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,what a very bad mistake is like
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.36,1:25:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.42,1:25:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to remind you guys
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.08,1:25:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,because you sit here and then you go to pieces
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.90,1:25:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I have to remind you
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.26,1:25:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.00,1:25:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.02,1:25:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,oh God
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.15,1:25:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,oh geez
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.14,1:25:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have to do this right
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.43,1:25:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,bypass her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.41,1:25:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,she's just taking a photo
Dialogue: 0,1:25:39.55,1:25:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.17,1:25:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.57,1:25:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.87,1:25:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.51,1:25:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he's with her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.17,1:25:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,oh he's with her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.23,1:25:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought she was the lady we just talked to
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.57,1:25:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.15,1:25:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we just talked to her
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.16,1:25:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.06,1:25:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,oh God
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.84,1:25:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.81,1:25:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,okay he has a question
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.77,1:26:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up being non-linear
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.03,1:26:00.79,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.79,1:26:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you doctor
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.26,1:26:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:26:10.10,1:26:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,all this work that you've done
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.94,1:26:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm just being introduced to it
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.78,1:26:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.30,1:26:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,just thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.88,1:26:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.20,1:26:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.36,1:26:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.00,1:26:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is it speak next to the telephone
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.00,1:26:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah come on up here
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.00,1:26:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be afraid of these
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.36,1:26:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,they can't hear you
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.36,1:26:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.36,1:26:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.36,1:26:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a simple question
Dialogue: 0,1:26:30.82,1:26:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but I don't know if it's been answered or asked before
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.40,1:26:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you know people smile
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.70,1:26:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you know children
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.00,1:26:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,adults
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.56,1:26:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's polite smiles
Dialogue: 0,1:26:39.42,1:26:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and then there's sometimes there's smiles
Dialogue: 0,1:26:41.62,1:26:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of times actually
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.84,1:26:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's smiles that you feel that go right to the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.94,1:26:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,can that be calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.60,1:26:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,can that smile
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.04,1:26:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,can that be calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:26:49.50,1:26:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,sure
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.50,1:26:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know what is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.08,1:26:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,do you know what the level is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:55.08,1:26:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,has it been calibrated
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.08,1:26:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,well it depends on the person
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.08,1:26:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and the occasion
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.08,1:27:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you know a smile like you said means different things in different circumstances
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.08,1:27:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:27:03.27,1:27:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,some people smile just because they're glad to be alive
Dialogue: 0,1:27:06.27,1:27:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and they have an upbeat attitude
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.34,1:27:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but is that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:09.34,1:27:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,there is
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.34,1:27:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean for myself I know I absolutely feel it
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.34,1:27:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,in my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.34,1:27:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,either coming to me or even leaving me
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.34,1:27:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,when I give smiles out
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.34,1:27:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,can that be calibrated then I guess a lot of times
Dialogue: 0,1:27:19.98,1:27:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess on my behalf
Dialogue: 0,1:27:21.98,1:27:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure what you mean but
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.98,1:27:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,smiling is a way of showing your appreciation for life
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.98,1:27:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and your joy at your own existence
Dialogue: 0,1:27:29.98,1:27:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that you want to share with others
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.98,1:27:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so a smile lights up other people
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.98,1:27:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and lights up the world
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.17,1:27:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're being of service to others you see
Dialogue: 0,1:27:39.17,1:27:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess what I was thinking about
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.36,1:27:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know the dog
Dialogue: 0,1:27:43.36,1:27:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,a love of the dog
Dialogue: 0,1:27:44.36,1:27:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and then when he's wagging his tail
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.36,1:27:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a little bit more
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.36,1:27:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,at 500
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.36,1:27:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,it does a smile
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.36,1:27:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,from the heart
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.36,1:27:52.36,Default,,0,0,0,,like that
Dialogue: 0,1:27:52.36,1:27:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,oh yes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:53.36,1:27:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,yes
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.36,1:27:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah of course it would sure
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.49,1:27:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.49,1:27:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,yep
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.49,1:27:59.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know I can hear wagging your tail
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.49,1:28:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:28:00.49,1:28:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.49,1:28:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:28:02.49,1:28:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.49,1:28:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.49,1:28:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's over 500
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.49,1:28:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't have a tail
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.49,1:28:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,so we have to smile
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.49,1:28:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,you know a dog can't smile
Dialogue: 0,1:28:09.49,1:28:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's got a tail
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.49,1:28:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we purr a lot though
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.03,1:28:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.03,1:28:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:18.03,1:28:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and once again thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.03,1:28:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.03,1:28:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for sharing
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.03,1:28:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing your
Dialogue: 0,1:28:22.03,1:28:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,sharing yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.03,1:28:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,with the
Dialogue: 0,1:28:24.03,1:28:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,world
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.03,1:28:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is a gift to the world
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.03,1:28:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,1:28:27.90,1:28:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.53,1:28:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.66,1:28:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.07,1:28:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,what's up doc
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.07,1:28:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a good one
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.42,1:28:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,give me a slug of that pepsi
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.42,1:28:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,they should give me free pepsi right
Dialogue: 0,1:28:47.61,1:28:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,for giving it air time
Dialogue: 0,1:28:50.96,1:28:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you can
Dialogue: 0,1:28:52.96,1:28:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been doing work
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.96,1:28:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on specialness
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.96,1:28:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,on the need to be special
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.96,1:28:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,lately
Dialogue: 0,1:28:56.96,1:28:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was hoping
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.96,1:28:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you could provide some feedback
Dialogue: 0,1:28:58.96,1:28:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,with that
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.96,1:29:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,because I have
Dialogue: 0,1:29:00.96,1:29:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,well it's just
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.96,1:29:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the specialness is
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.96,1:29:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.96,1:29:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,feeling unique
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.96,1:29:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:29:05.96,1:29:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,giving the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:29:06.96,1:29:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a boost
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.96,1:29:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:29:08.96,1:29:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,hates to be
Dialogue: 0,1:29:10.25,1:29:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.25,1:29:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and nobody
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.25,1:29:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you learn
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.25,1:29:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to
